---
title: Beef, Pork & Halloumi Cheeseburger with Fries, Truffle Mayo & Caramelised Onion
description: Everyone loves a cheeseburger, so we’re offering up one of our own. The spiced beef and pork patties and haloumi get cheesy when cooked with melted Cheddar cheese on the top and served with golden fries with truffle mayo for dipping. It’s a much-loved dish for a reason!
